Introduction:

The project focuses on digital literacy and creating a professional online presence as a Student Digital Ambassador. In today’s digital world, it is vital for a person to be digitally literate and able to use digital tools effectively and safely. There are five tasks to be completed for this project, covering essential areas such as digital literacy awareness, building a digital portfolio, coding platforms, professional online communication, and safe practices against cybercrime.
During the project, I got to experience a variety of digital platforms and tools, create informative content, and understand how to communicate professionally online. In addition, the project helped me comprehend the significance of online safety and digital literacy. Therefore, this project is designed to ensure that students are digitally literate and able to confidently use digital tools and maintain a strong and professional online presence.

