For Task 1 of the project, I created a Digital Literacy Awareness Infographic using Prezi. Prezi is a presentation tool that enables users to create visually appealing and creative content. It is a powerful tool for creating content that can be presented effectively.
My infographic presentation focuses on creating awareness about digital literacy and its significance for students. It covers essential areas such as digital literacy, digital tools for students, and safe internet practices. It also demonstrates how digital literacy is effective in communication, online safety, and creating a professional online presence.
During the creation of the infographic, it was interesting to arrange the content in such a way that it is visually appealing and easy to comprehend. However, it was slightly challenging to ensure the right amount of content and design without making it too crowded.
Overall, the task helped me enhance my creativity and comprehend the importance of effectively communicating crucial information through digital media.

