This project has been highly beneficial in the sense that I have gained valuable insights into digital literacy and its importance in the present world. I have also gained knowledge on how to use digital platforms through the five tasks. I have also gained knowledge about the importance of digital literacy and the various practices to be followed while using digital platforms. This project has also helped me in the development of both technical and communication skills. I have also gained confidence to use digital platforms in a more professional way. This project has prepared me to be more aware, skilled, and professional in the digital world.

